up semi-finals. March 18, 2018 In "Sports" Eden Hazard is expected to operate in an unusual centre-forward role after Chelsea boss Antonio Conte left Olivier Giroud and Alvaro Morata on the bench for Tuesday's Champions League last 16, first leg against Barcelona. February 20, 2018 In "Sports" After scoring twice in Chelsea’s 4-1 win over Arsenal in the 2019 UEFA Europa League final match on Wednesday, Belgium’s Eden Hazard said he has now found the right moment. May 30, 2019 In "News"